ps://qxlpgsghajxthihcpqwr.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/portfolio-images/0.28070959599832657.png', ARRAY['php','laravel','react js'], 'fullstack', 'https://comathedu.id/', 'https://comathedu.id/', true, ARRAY['Comprehensive UTBK & SNBT tryouts','In-depth answer explanations','High-quality learning videos','Personalized PTN (public university) recommendations'], '2025-12-17 17:58:33.468742+00');